                    Section: 6 - Premium Themes, Frameworks and Child Themes
1 - Why Premium Themes?
Premium themes are themes that cost money
Premium themes are under constant development with regular updates.
Under Appearence -> Themes you can search for themes including premium themes
GPL themes are also available for WP
Themes -
 - Studiopress -- http://my.studiopress.com/themes/
